{
  "texts": [
    "Section 3 reviews the Sieve 2SLS estimator and presents generalization bounds highlighting the role of spectral features.",
    "Section 4 shows how to learn such features via a contrastive loss and connects this to the method of [36].",
    "Section 5 presents a practical procedure to estimate the spectral properties from data, enabling an empirical diagnosis of our taxonomy.",
    "Section 6 provides synthetic experiments, including an application to the dSprites dataset, that validate our theoretical taxonomy.",
    "Proofs are deferred to the Appendix."
  ]
}